name: Healthier Lemon Zucchini Bread
author: DAWERI
summary: A healthier alternative to some of the other zucchini breads out there that still tastes great!
ingredients: ½ cup agave nectar, or more to taste
directions: Preheat oven to 325 degrees F (165 degrees C)
Beat zucchini, agave nectar, egg, coconut oil, applesauce, lemon juice, and lemon zest together with an electric mixer in a bowl until smooth
Whisk flour, cinnamon, salt, baking soda, and baking powder together in a bowl; mix into zucchini mixture until batter is just combined
Pour batter into the prepared loaf pans
Bake in the preheated oven until a knife inserted in the center comes out clean, 30 to 40 minutes
Cool bread in pans for 10 minutes before turning onto a wire rack to cool completely
